column5: anybody on here fish in quebec?
I do. My camp is in N/W QC west of Rouyn Noranda, headed up this week to do some fishin.'
how about the gatineau to maniwaki area?
Yep  Laniel,top end of Kipawa.Heading up in a couple weeks.   Cant wait!!!
Oh yes Laniel, lovely place. I really need to get back up there and catch some of those monster Kipawa Walleyes.

Ive been here many times, we used to go as a group of about 10 years ago when i was younger, and went back about 4 years ago with a few family members and it conjured up some awesome memories. I dont remember the name of the camp, its on lac remigny  Lake Remigny
Yeppers....Been fishin' up there the past couple of weeks now

Oh Ya.  St.Lawrence River  Lac St.Pierre  Richelieu River  Lake Massawippi  Lake Memphremagog  St.Alexis des Monts  La Tuques  Rivieres St.Maurices  Lake Champlain  Rivieres des Milles Iles  Ferme Neuve Mont-Laurier  and many more to discover just need more holidays.  Mike
